changelog:
Support for voice or video chat using Google Talk.[72]
Open Accessory Library support. Open Accessory was introduced in 3.1 (Honeycomb) but the Open Accessory Library grants 2.3.4 added support when connecting to a USB peripheral with compatible software and a compatible application on the device.[73]
Switched the default encryption for SSL from AES256-SHA to RC4-MD5.[74][75]
Fixed a spontaneous reboot on Samsung Galaxy S Plus.
